featured_reviews.review_id:
The Masjid is well constructed.
If you are planning to visit here with a car its quite better to park the car on the side of the highways as the path to the Masjid is quite conjested with the other cars parked outside the home.
Its nice to see many small children coming to pray from the nearby homes.
The rest room is well maintained too.
